They framed me.

51
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,650
They want to take my place!

52
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:29,350
Miss Rong,

53
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,800
we can't let this matter
ruin the affection

54
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,079
