78
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:08,070
Since ancient times,
fine swords are gifted to heroes.

79
00:04:08,070 --> 00:04:09,800
From now on, whoever you fancy,

80
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,520
or whatever treasure you desire,

81
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,430
